  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency prettier to v1.7.4",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier\">prettier</a> from <code>v1.7.0</code> to <code>v1.7.4</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>prettier/prettier</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"174\">1.7.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/33a1f59e01118ef572a5f5155e0c45e84a78b4ed\"><code>33a1f59</code></a> Ensure package is published from dist/ with correct version number (#&#8203;2963)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/fcdf6b58069f51ed6d34696b7c0ee9679bd3e486\"><code>fcdf6b5</code></a> Add test for #&#8203;2880 (#&#8203;2959)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/d9737e6ffaa3f7d9ebeb900b1fa59c07b4f77301\"><code>d9737e6</code></a> test: fix snapshots (#&#8203;2957)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/7770356a519399dcbf8eda1b04c0c0560e6f2573\"><code>7770356</code></a> test(integration): update title and catch all outputs (#&#8203;2951)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/43cb08c45cddd8bf44bbbae1adf87a0eaf8e1bd6\"><code>43cb08c</code></a> Make production tests always run against dist/ (attempt 2) (#&#8203;2942)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/26254ece0fe02809903482bd58dc246eecb14aed\"><code>26254ec</code></a> chore(deps): pin dependencies (#&#8203;2953)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/2466ce11a5233a88b1682ef70b04c1993c2bdda0\"><code>2466ce1</code></a> Force template literals to break after &#x60; for sytled-components (#&#8203;2926)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/64ec692b922da81cfbfacd9ae2d66f62454fbca9\"><code>64ec692</code></a> Mention labels docs in CONTRIBUTING.md (#&#8203;2950)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/c7f9bb5731d7edb34585afec4b079a1605c66945\"><code>c7f9bb5</code></a> chore(deps): update cosmiconfig to v3.1.0 (#&#8203;2952)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/a6096ee7996378809a6a3d5a7ee01101afe66853\"><code>a6096ee</code></a> Respect --stdin-filepath, regardless of config source (#&#8203;2948)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/3329ee022fd5a685f06022049b15c4985fb727c5\"><code>3329ee0</code></a> Upgrade prettier to 1.7.3 (#&#8203;2940)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/099cf760d03ef7a94db485aa3d486ec7bdafb150\"><code>099cf76</code></a> Update ISSUE_TEMPLATE to 1.7.3</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"173\">1.7.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/ecf0281b31f90ea6e1a6a44713e9ec1f023832a7\"><code>ecf0281</code></a> 1.7.3</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/808dc4e7e3fb66b028a6d2d7ce5619aae4e559ab\"><code>808dc4e</code></a> Add missing quote in README.md</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/9d448fb217016d5b0abd5a23d441b8fc9551144f\"><code>9d448fb</code></a> Try to fix website deploy</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/fa882b26aff8ed91adb2636d8abef89b73d23f44\"><code>fa882b2</code></a> Fix Travis production builds (#&#8203;2933)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/63916beebba738f344d2f5612eee19cd023cc1d5\"><code>63916be</code></a> Try to fix cosmiconfig in the built version of Prettier (#&#8203;2930)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/0d756080b50f518578dda3a23bd4ce5076cd2e00\"><code>0d75608</code></a> fix: ignore and show warning for unknown option from config file (#&#8203;2929)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/51d123b3f1ff52060b344d15080cacc87f313df9\"><code>51d123b</code></a> Update postcss-values-parser (#&#8203;2928)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/3c91c2ab42dbf8947d0004052351387b06fae4b5\"><code>3c91c2a</code></a> Fix unit tests on Windows (#&#8203;2922)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/264ec70999e69fa46a7ef9d7f62b917ffd60bdb6\"><code>264ec70</code></a> Don&#x27;t use parens with optional chaining meber expressions (#&#8203;2921)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/ae21d6038686c867e95b336460f5ca2ecb25c278\"><code>ae21d60</code></a> Recommend pinning prettier version (#&#8203;2920)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"172\">1.7.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/75781a6d16e6f8aa86711f9bcd02cb2e1c60c9db\"><code>75781a6</code></a> 1.7.2</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/038d02b3e24ee6cfdbade639242d666c54dc87ce\"><code>038d02b</code></a> Revert &quot;Fix line break in test declarations with a single argument function declaration&quot; (#&#8203;2912)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/0313ce6299e59c038208bab27d75d98342695969\"><code>0313ce6</code></a> Fix the playground for 1.7.1</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"171\">1.7.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/c2bc33b3ad9882aa795a8fa8a15b5fd1629765da\"><code>c2bc33b</code></a> 1.7.1</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/11a7b8d308bdf4f7896f939d652c5795d34608f4\"><code>11a7b8d</code></a> Fix printing of comments between decorators and method names (#&#8203;2906)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/6179d92518a3bbc43043baf354cb19da93a50de8\"><code>6179d92</code></a> Fix editor styles for blank playgrounds (#&#8203;2904)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/f77e471b0c485e7b179a7e9f40829f92909ef7b2\"><code>f77e471</code></a> Upgrade to ts2.5.3-insiders (#&#8203;2842)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/3703cb5b07a158c507b49c23ef5f7b4abb8a41fe\"><code>3703cb5</code></a> Fix line break in test declarations with a single argument function declaration (#&#8203;2877)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/88049a3d6bc742566d865f6a01f8f0f7ad4541bf\"><code>88049a3</code></a> Keep original empty lines in argument list (#&#8203;2763)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/daef1441023fe5b5b014b2b51fe063163eab1484\"><code>daef144</code></a> Support fit(), xit(), it.only(), etc (#&#8203;2900)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/e1c2085d2ee4a16278bacd4d7710dc27885ac4e1\"><code>e1c2085</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;2888 from motiz88/fix-2593</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/c6bac7cfe698fd9d68ce962b214befb81dff650b\"><code>c6bac7c</code></a> Split Less and SCSS parsing into different parsers (#&#8203;2844)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/70f5165bb14b0435129926cee69a4271fcf9cf67\"><code>70f5165</code></a> fix(typescript): allow symbol type (#&#8203;2899)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/630ea58a50d8cdeb5ec73fa4ba9cda7f92480b57\"><code>630ea58</code></a> refactor: use custom error (#&#8203;2896)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/4435ecbc7bb606235a16664bd4549d03c96a932c\"><code>4435ecb</code></a> fix(cli): validate options for every <code>config-precedence</code> (#&#8203;2894)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/798bdb0e6a219708a2c94f0be92648ca5c09f311\"><code>798bdb0</code></a> We do not need to have a reference to the toolbox-companion since we (#&#8203;2892)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/d0a622ffa837b2f3d3a4344a96835af4dadeae1c\"><code>d0a622f</code></a> fix: do not print stack trace for invalid option (#&#8203;2895)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/5e146cdabeb25fa1bfb94ac9b0a9efa497bfcf5b\"><code>5e146cd</code></a> Use semicolons in Flow interface-like bodies (#&#8203;2593)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/cd4d4e7273b1732caff2b8006edd9c69336a4504\"><code>cd4d4e7</code></a> Don&#x27;t lowercase SCSS placeholder selectors (#&#8203;2876)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/184e368a9ac0fd8cc4195fec06378f3829ad7a68\"><code>184e368</code></a> feat: support detailed <code>--help</code> (#&#8203;2847)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/9b0d6b8de05bba57eabda6280b934a8138626651\"><code>9b0d6b8</code></a> Fix different precedence binary expression when inlining (#&#8203;2827)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/2be986d0d7261463b7c001906bb917c6fa1dfa96\"><code>2be986d</code></a> Add support for ClassPrivateProperty (#&#8203;2837)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/68d1b56696005821178b45437629c439e9c110c1\"><code>68d1b56</code></a> Comment out config file extensions docs until next release</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/f6356ae94c12ad17122f681530a01abb623bbc16\"><code>f6356ae</code></a> chore: add prettier-stylelint to the related projects (#&#8203;2859)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/eb776b7635ad9b75eb0fd80d43434cd072566475\"><code>eb776b7</code></a> Update cosmiconfig to 3.0.1 to avoid memory leak (#&#8203;2848)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/592f99fde69880c69fadb3887db911d87fa306a6\"><code>592f99f</code></a> Enable cosmiconfig rcExtensions (#&#8203;2749)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/ed67690925ecd7172eacfcf7ec9f3145ef6571f6\"><code>ed67690</code></a> Fix playground for the next release</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/48899289da0d4103343055589b72b19d7074ad0d\"><code>4889928</code></a> Upgrade cosmiconfig to v3, remove hardcoded combinatoric problem (#&#8203;2843)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/2c59fb2f07174223251ec198f5215049d3773875\"><code>2c59fb2</code></a> Upgrade prettier dependency to 1.7.0, fix lint (#&#8203;2821)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/fb55367633bbf57e8c61cf64fa936a0f7c344e8c\"><code>fb55367</code></a> Don&#x27;t lowercase Less variables when parsed with SCSS parser (#&#8203;2833)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/23041e2113cb4bf9bc7ff773cccaa7b1ef93ef1c\"><code>23041e2</code></a> Don&#x27;t lowercase <code>&amp;class</code> in SCSS/Less selectors (#&#8203;2834)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/5bd8ca472b64ba2f215edf87f20ee3350db048ed\"><code>5bd8ca4</code></a> Bump Babylon (#&#8203;2831)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/06c9127f022642cbf6d47fd2bef0d74b5cbc17a5\"><code>06c9127</code></a> Update instructions for running tests against dist</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/ec4abdfb1e47d9caef7e902b321927ac45fbe90a\"><code>ec4abdf</code></a> Don&#x27;t lowercase CSS custom media names (#&#8203;2822)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/219acfe0f80218f73b28b8d11db46ac52de62592\"><code>219acfe</code></a> Fix playground error</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier/commit/2ef7173f13ab3e25d9370ee8061666b8d23b863b\"><code>2ef7173</code></a> Fix playground button color</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
